NEALE, Inc., et al., Appellants, v. ELECTRICAL PRODUCTS CORPORATION, a Corporation, Appellee. No. 6629. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 12, 1931. For former opinion, see 48 F.(2d) 824.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and JAMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
